Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在精灵球里的宠物 简称宠物小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这星球上非常不可思议的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的种类有 一百 两百 三百…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也许会比这更多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精灵与人类作为朋友与伙伴齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时也会作为敌人而对立
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们居于在世界的各处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来这位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真新镇的小智
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了成为小精灵大师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断对战与收服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续着自己的修行之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与小精灵的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与小精灵的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此 无数的故事相继而生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那是从很遥远 很遥远的过去开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}『很久以前…还没有小精灵球的时代…』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波导之力 存于我心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了 鲁卡利欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量庞大的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它们交手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一人无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争真的已经不可避免了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这里的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命运与这城堡是连在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁卡利欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经抛弃了那座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会再回到那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树…创世之树…正在哭泣着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳女王明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是波导使者亚伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与梦幻让创世之树发出它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨与愤怒也平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精灵们也回到了自己生活地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是这片大地也恢复了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此亚伦就被人们称为「波导的勇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再给我讲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波导的勇者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,800)}『然后 现在…』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了成为小精灵大师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而持续旅行的小智一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了这座奥尔多兰城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了参加赞颂波导的勇者亚伦而举行的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城内的小精灵对战中获胜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会被尊为今年的「波导的勇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服装的话 不穿上古代的衣服是不能参加的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 没带这种衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里已经准备好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还有勇者的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话也要把皮卡丘打扮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在这里面选吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪件比较好呢 眼花缭乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的服装在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精灵对战差不多要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 皮卡丘 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁大家乐此不疲的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个城堡的小精灵都抓走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 要换身衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打扮成什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个超棒耶 啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔多兰城的城主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾琳殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下 真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为赞颂拯救世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波导的勇者——亚伦举行的小精灵对战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:25.24,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,光る　大地に立ち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:31.30,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠の　バトル誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:37.27,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顔　ちょっぴり涙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:43.33,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,みんな　忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:49.26,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,想いは　距離を飛び越え
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:58.06,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,今　君に届く　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.23,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,ウーイエ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.87,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,GANGAN　進め　風切って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.87,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,GANGAN　行くゼ　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:10.01,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,完全·燃焼　YES, I'm OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:10.99,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,ウーイエ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.72,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,DONDON　パワー　盛り上がって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.70,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,DONDON　勇気湧いてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:21.59,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,限りない　力を信じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.26,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,ウーイエ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.99,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,GANGAN　進め　風切って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.90,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,GANGAN　行くゼ　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:47.07,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,完全·燃焼　YES, I'm OK!
