Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.41,1:09:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.75,1:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 沙漠兽
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.32,1:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙漠兽 导弹针
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.00,1:09:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没效果
