Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.17,1:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.12,1:09:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武藏
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.55,1:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小次…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.39,1:10:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风铃铃 你自己快逃
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.00,1:10:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.87,1:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又来了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.45,1:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.40,1:10:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.17,1:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.01,1:11:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班克斯 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.18,1:11:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是创世之树类似于白血球的物体
